Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs18}請勿以本片圖利  否則月亮會懲罰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.87,0:00:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美麗的地球啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來把她變得更美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來  地球將變成我的囊中物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.77,0:01:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}YMP字幕組製作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.77,0:01:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}片源: 貓某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}時間軸: Xel'Naga
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.74,0:01:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}翻譯: 小砂 & Fuuko
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.74,0:01:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}校譯: Switch & jechmh
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a5}{\fs14}{\fad(120,120)}後期製作: 貓某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.92,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ごめんね　素直じゃなくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.38,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢の中なら言える
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.76,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思考回路はショート寸前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.64,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今すぐ會いたいよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.39,0:02:28.48,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泣きたくなるよな moonlight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.94,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電話もできない midnight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.36,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,だって純情　どうしよう?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.49,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ハートは万華鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:45.58,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月の光に導かれ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.04,0:02:52.21,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何度も巡り會う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.80,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星座のまたたき數え
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.22,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占う戀のゆくえ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.64,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同じ地球に生まれたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.97,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Miracle Romance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.27,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信じているの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.60,OpJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Miracle Romance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.20,0:02:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(120,120)}美少女戰士  Sailormoon S  劇場版\N竹姬的戀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起我並不直率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在夢中才能表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.55,0:02:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在思緒錯亂之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在就好想見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.39,0:02:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人想哭泣的 moonlight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這通不了電話的 midnight
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的純情  該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.48,0:02:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心就如萬花筒一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮的光芒  引導著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.04,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與你相會無數次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,細數星宿的閃爍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占卜戀愛的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能生於同一個國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便是奇蹟的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是如此相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇蹟的浪漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}以探查新月球為目標的月球開拓計劃{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.99,0:03:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}太空人名單之中有一位眾所矚目的日本女性  名夜竹姬子小姐{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.79,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}目前正在NASA忙碌於發射前的準備工作{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}接下來請跟著記者體驗月球開拓計畫的模擬訓練…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇  那艘太空船要飛去月球耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.97,0:03:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也好想搭那個  跟小衛去月球旅行喲～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.47,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳又在說什麼不正經的鬼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都已經是國中最後一個寒假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中入學考試如果不準備的話  這樣不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼  露娜妳又沒有談過戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戀愛中的女人是怎樣的心情  妳才不會了解呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我就是…哈啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有談過戀愛嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜  妳怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…昨天開始吧  好像有點感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔  我想我先回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我陪妳一起回去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.18,0:04:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以自己走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.01,0:04:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿特米斯你不需要小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渾、渾蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳醒來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要起來比較好  妳還在發燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.25,0:05:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天晚上好好安靜地睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}這個人…整晚都待在我身邊…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}居然為了我…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}為了這樣的我…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦  露娜呢!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她昨天一直沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.94,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會那時候就不舒服  在哪裡病倒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知道就送她回來的!  我就說嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她該不會是離家出走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔  妳有沒有想到什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有欺負她啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家才不會欺負露娜呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.96,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是不是對露娜惡言相向啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨手笨腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粗心大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛哭鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被惡言相向的明明就是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小麗真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可不是吵架的時候!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家分頭找她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有食慾的話  吃點東西比較好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒好像好多了呢  真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔  早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子  妳回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼時候到日本的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搭早上第一班的飛機回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.49,0:08:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月球開拓計畫的新聞  你看到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說了  恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年沒回到日本了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼變吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前兩天晚上  我觀測到一顆新的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯  它就在月球的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就將它命名為「冰雪竹姬」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是在看月亮啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過說也奇怪  NASA那邊居然沒聽說這個消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你確定你沒看錯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有看錯  我確實看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還發現這個  很可能是它一部分的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現彗星的那天晚上撿到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.87,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是彗星馬上就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太空開拓企業的同仁都不相信彗星的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但妳是相信我的  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的看到了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.71,0:09:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前你說月亮上有個女神時  大家都在笑你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.39,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對宇宙似乎抱持太多浪漫的幻想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是每當我眺望月亮的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就可以感覺到神秘能量的存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聽起來實在不太像是學科學的人會說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不相信我就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.07,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔!  你從小時候就很優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.57,0:09:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可是擁有物理學、生物學、醫學  還有宇宙工學等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.58,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許多學位的博士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都期待你會成為太空人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為何還要講這些不切實際的東西呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思  妳可以回去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.06,0:10:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我利用一星期的假期…為了和你見面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠從美國的麻州…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地飛回來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.99,0:10:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.95,0:10:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我不能誠實一點地為她高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.05,0:10:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛上太空是她最大的心願  好不容易美夢成真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了  妳叫什麼名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.85,0:10:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}啊  我不能開口說話呀{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小黑?  小玉?  應該也不是三毛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你額頭上有個新月…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Moon?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.08,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}(拉丁文中的月亮為Luna)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此  妳叫做露娜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}沒錯!{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫妳取露娜這麼時髦的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的主人想必是個很有品味的人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}(有- 品- 味- )
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要來點星星糖嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}(原文為「金平糖」，こんぺいとう)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星星糖就好像流星一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.36,0:11:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果邊吃邊許願  總有一天一定會見到竹姬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從小我就這樣相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.99,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很蠢吧  居然相信月亮上有位神秘的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  妳也相信啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:11:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前有個傳說叫做「竹取物語」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.46,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得故事裡的竹姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像真的在月亮上存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}這心動的感覺是什麼?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}這種感覺…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}是第一次…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美麗的地球啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.68,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我長久以來渴望的寶物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要成為我的囊中物了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可愛的雪之舞姬們啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把地球變成一片冰雪吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}Mercury Star Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,300)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}Mars Star Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}Jupiter Star Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}Venus Star Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}Uranus Planet Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.10,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H96BB00&}Neptune Planet Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H96BB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFF8080&}Pluto Planet Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFF8080&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}World…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}{\fad(0,200)}Shaking!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}Supreme…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Thunder!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}Crescent…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Beam!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙真噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}Bubble…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,300)}Spray!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}Fire…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Soul!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.12,0:18:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小小兔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&CA69FE&}Moon Prism Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.41,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&CA69FE&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Cosmic Power～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我慢著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開心的寒假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.51,0:19:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然把人群跟街道都冰封  我絕不原諒你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不原諒你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.35,0:19:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛與正義的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水手服美少女戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與Sailor Chibi Moon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會代替月亮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懲罰你!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.26,0:20:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼玩意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.80,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再轉下去的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會頭暈的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sailor Moon!  千萬不能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭昏啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本尊就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.91,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇啊～猜錯了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕老公公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕快樂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新年快樂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚禮服假面!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下著雪的北國冬日是非常嚴寒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是  將大地覆上銀白的雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是在冬日相會的美麗戀人們一樣啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs18}{\b1}{\c&HFFFF00&}?{\b0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sailor Moon  趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.85,0:21:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.96,0:22:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon Spiral…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Heart…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.96,0:22:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,200)}Attack!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.70,0:22:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恢復正常了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.58,0:23:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道地球上有人礙事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.42,0:23:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪之舞姬啊  有找到掉在日本地區的結晶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.22,0:23:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那結晶可以將整個世界冰封起來…快找出來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.61,0:23:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在很久以前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.32,0:23:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我試圖接近地球的時候  有一道光將我彈開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.32,0:23:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之後我歷經了長久的旅途又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不能著急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.08,0:23:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只需改變奪取地球的計畫就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.92,0:23:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在沒人察覺的情況下  逐漸將地球納入我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.17,0:23:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要找到那個結晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.57,0:24:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙究竟是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.07,0:24:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侵略地球的新敵人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.20,0:24:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何  千萬不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.49,0:24:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  是露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.42,0:24:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.84,0:24:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害我擔心了好久喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.55,0:24:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦  那個緞帶是哪來的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.64,0:24:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.52,0:24:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要再來玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.52,0:24:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不管這個  我聽說有個不明彗星正在接近地球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.11,0:24:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彗星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.78,0:24:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.91,0:25:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是並沒有找到露娜所說的那個彗星啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.25,0:25:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果亞美的電腦偵測不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.79,0:25:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之後也沒有其他異常事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許那奇怪的敵人就這樣消失了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.09,0:25:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起我遲到了～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.30,0:25:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳啊  真是遲到大王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.47,0:25:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎喲  人家在路上遇到一個好帥的男生～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.89,0:25:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦  露娜呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.72,0:25:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔  好像有事的樣子  她說她不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.39,0:25:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近露娜變得好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.65,0:25:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直吃星星糖  還讀了好多醫生的書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.86,0:25:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說起來  她這幾天才到我家來借醫學用書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.45,0:25:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我前天在太空開拓企業的天文台附近看到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.58,0:25:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有叫她  但她好像沒聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.00,0:25:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.04,0:25:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有那個黃色緞帶  不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.79,0:25:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像都沒叫我要唸書什麼囉囉嗦嗦的了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.71,0:25:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實是很奇怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.38,0:25:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好燙～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.76,0:25:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.52,0:26:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.81,0:26:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是生什麼病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.33,0:26:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思喔～小貓咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.04,0:26:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳今天別打擾他  回家去好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.84,0:26:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}打擾!?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.71,0:26:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}因為…我只是一隻貓…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.22,0:26:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜從她失蹤那時候開始就變得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.64,0:26:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道是怎麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.48,0:26:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.44,0:26:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許露娜只是想要自己的自由時間而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.36,0:26:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直黏著她或是問東問西  不覺得她有點可憐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.61,0:26:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直黏著?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.53,0:27:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小衛  所以…你是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.37,0:27:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了  我在小衛身旁的時候  你一定也覺得我很黏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.24,0:27:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等～小兔子  我並不是這個意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.08,0:27:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}如果我是人類的話  就可以照顧翔了…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.01,0:27:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜  妳誤會了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.51,0:27:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我總是黏著你…很煩人不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.39,0:27:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可從不認為小兔子很煩人啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.56,0:27:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.68,0:27:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.06,0:27:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小衛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.35,0:27:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.76,0:27:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔  妳聞起來好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.34,0:28:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是乾燥花的香味喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.68,0:28:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…妳跟小衛通常都聊些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.77,0:28:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各式各樣的話題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.40,0:28:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過小衛總是看很難的書  很多時候我也搭不上話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.15,0:28:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是  他感興趣的話題總是很努力地說給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.37,0:28:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.45,0:28:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.75,0:28:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在沙發上一下子就睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:33.71,0:28:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.21,0:28:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒…沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.38,0:28:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會那麼自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.80,0:28:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為跟我在一起很輕鬆的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.55,0:28:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小衛睡著的樣子好可愛喔  就像小孩子一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.52,0:28:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…接吻是怎樣的滋味?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.23,0:28:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個啊  很甜很甜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.86,0:29:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像要融化了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.61,0:29:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很甜很甜…就好像要融化了一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.13,0:29:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小衛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.77,0:29:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜  妳來啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.02,0:29:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.28,0:29:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾經夢想成為一個太空人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.86,0:29:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但由於先天身體虛弱  只好放棄了我的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.08,0:29:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.33,0:29:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的身體已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.96,0:30:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我可以看著姬子起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.01,0:30:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的夢想就由她來實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.43,0:30:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜也跟我一起祈禱她飛行順利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.18,0:30:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.06,0:30:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然聽不懂  但我覺得露娜妳真是隻善解人意的貓咪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.48,0:30:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從太空看地球跟月球一定很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.74,0:30:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想讓妳看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.24,0:30:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.08,0:30:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜妳好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.25,0:30:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聞起來好舒服的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.59,0:30:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}小衛睡著的樣子好可愛喔  就像小孩子一樣{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.42,0:30:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}我也好想…跟你一起去宇宙{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.87,0:31:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了～我看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.00,0:31:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一大早就心花怒放往外跑的露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.52,0:31:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.48,0:31:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是戀愛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.05,0:31:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戀愛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.92,0:31:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜終於戀愛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.47,0:31:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是還沒有證據啊  不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.39,0:31:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個黃色緞帶!  一定是戀愛了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.31,0:31:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也這樣覺得!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.03,0:31:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託  妳們也考慮一下阿特米斯的心情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.28,0:31:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.16,0:31:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?  怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.03,0:31:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?  小兔…難道妳不知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.45,0:31:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?  什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.33,0:32:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是阿特米斯對露娜的心意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.79,0:32:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他愛上她啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.13,0:32:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳現在才發現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.05,0:32:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直以為他們只是很好的朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.42,0:32:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真遲鈍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.97,0:32:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戀愛啊  真令人羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.68,0:32:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可是考生呢  沒時間談戀愛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.81,0:32:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不一樣喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.52,0:32:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有小衛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.69,0:32:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙真煩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.17,0:32:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有夠囂張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.94,0:32:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是啊  考完之後我也好想談一場很棒的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.57,0:32:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.87,0:32:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這讓我想起了學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.20,0:32:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想再見他一面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.91,0:32:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的初戀情人到底在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:40.96,0:32:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也有同感…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:49.09,0:32:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙就再也沒出現過了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.93,0:32:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風平浪靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是暴風雨前的寧靜呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.51,0:32:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遙  妳有感覺到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.85,0:33:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  沒什麼  但我有種預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.44,0:33:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是  但什麼也感覺不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.86,0:33:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間就像是停止了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.65,0:33:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水手戰士們  還搞不清楚狀況嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.84,0:33:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.11,0:33:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.89,0:33:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜  如果妳在擔心什麼事的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.31,0:33:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思  我在趕時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.44,0:33:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}對不起  阿特米斯{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.92,0:34:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}露娜愛上的難道就是…那個人嗎?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.84,0:34:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔  我今天就要離開日本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.43,0:34:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  是今天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:22.68,0:34:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預祝妳成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.43,0:34:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.73,0:34:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.23,0:34:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我從太空回來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.77,0:34:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會…一直待在你身邊的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.40,0:34:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.70,0:34:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳和我截然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.03,0:34:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想法更是天差地別…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:43.95,0:34:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對妳而言  月亮只是漂浮在太空裡的一個物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.96,0:34:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不這麼想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.67,0:34:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳一定會找到更適合妳的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.18,0:34:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.47,0:35:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你眼中是這樣的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.89,0:35:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是這樣看待我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.10,0:35:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.86,0:35:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.61,0:35:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我無法感受到月亮上像竹姬般的神秘生命力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.53,0:35:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.27,0:35:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說夠了沒?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.93,0:35:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}翔…他其實…很愛姬子的…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.19,0:35:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.44,0:35:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.19,0:35:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.28,0:36:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔他…對姬子隱瞞他的病情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.88,0:36:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.24,0:36:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明就愛著姬子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.12,0:36:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:08.50,0:36:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔  雖然我只是一隻貓  但我覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.13,0:36:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許可以和他心靈相通  就像命中註定的人那樣也說不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.51,0:36:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的這樣覺得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.01,0:36:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過…對他而言的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.14,0:36:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.73,0:36:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好想變成人類的女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.73,0:36:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是人類的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.61,0:36:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我能夠以人類的身分在他身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.15,0:36:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少可以對他說出我的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.20,0:36:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不會像現在這麼難過了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.04,0:36:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.09,0:37:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.31,0:37:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:26.24,0:37:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這結晶在吸取你的能量之後  好像變得更強大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.08,0:37:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是那顆彗星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:35.54,0:37:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰雪竹姬!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.67,0:37:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰雪竹姬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.80,0:37:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真美的名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.51,0:37:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯  我的分身正在緩緩地接近地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.39,0:37:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.56,0:37:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在地球被冰凍的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.43,0:37:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將變成我美麗的收藏品之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.03,0:38:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到頭來敵人還是不肯放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.90,0:38:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得讓大家知道!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.78,0:38:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔會那麼痛苦  全是因為那顆彗星的結晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.62,0:38:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過已經不要緊了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.83,0:38:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.67,0:38:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.46,0:38:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要那結晶存在  妖氣就無法消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.55,0:38:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正是大好時機  把地球化為美麗的冰雪世界吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.79,0:38:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.62,0:38:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前我在文獻上看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.91,0:39:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太古以前  有一顆邪惡之星四處散播她的冰晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.50,0:39:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些水晶將地球冰封  並讓大地陷入黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.76,0:39:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是  集結偉大的愛與友情之「魔幻銀水晶」的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.47,0:39:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驅逐了黑暗  拯救了地球!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.81,0:39:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文獻上是這樣記載的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.23,0:39:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪惡之星  該不會就是露娜所說的那顆彗星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.19,0:39:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛與友情之「魔幻銀水晶」的力量  指的又是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:23.53,0:39:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之  來者不善的彗星經過長時間之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.94,0:39:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有可能已準備好要來侵略地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.28,0:39:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不容許這種事發生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.12,0:39:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}(宇宙開拓企業)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:35.41,0:39:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼  多保重身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.96,0:39:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.46,0:39:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.13,0:39:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:43.88,0:39:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  這隻貓咪!  是你家的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.09,0:39:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子小姐  請將月球開拓計畫延期好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.55,0:39:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.06,0:39:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個彗星正在接近地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.97,0:39:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且彗星上有一個冰之魔女!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.23,0:40:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.06,0:40:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許妳不相信我  可是她正準備要冰凍地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.03,0:40:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛到太空太危險了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.74,0:40:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.78,0:40:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.78,0:40:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在可是科技當道的時代  請別跟我說那些幻想的東西!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.12,0:40:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.88,0:40:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.55,0:40:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果讓他遇見夢中的竹姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.76,0:40:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來  就有力量可以對抗邪惡的妖氣了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.30,0:40:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹姬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.01,0:40:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我是人類女孩的話  就可以為了他變成竹姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.44,0:40:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜  就算妳變成人類  妳跟翔也不能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.65,0:40:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會怎樣都無所謂  只要可以救翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.70,0:40:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能見到他從小夢寐以求的竹姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.24,0:40:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會勇氣大增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.25,0:41:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許就會有力量來抵抗妖氣了也說不定!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.00,0:41:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過  貓怎麼可能變成人類的樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.30,0:41:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}全世界籠罩於異常的極地氣候  就連非洲大草原…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.52,0:41:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.06,0:41:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是那傢伙做的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.23,0:41:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}日本全國今晚及明天將有暴風雪…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.06,0:41:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:27.02,0:41:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到敵人的基地了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.90,0:42:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切全都結成冰了呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.41,0:42:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由新時代引領  Sailor Uranus  華麗而活躍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:21.25,0:42:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣地  由新時代引領  Sailor Neptune  優雅而活躍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.92,0:42:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我乃掌管時間的Sailor Pluto
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.67,0:42:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不容許妳對地球為所欲為!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:35.43,0:42:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於出現啦  水手戰士們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.76,0:42:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但已經太遲了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.73,0:42:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H96BB00&}Deep…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.11,0:42:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H96BB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Submerge!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.72,0:43:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}World…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.10,0:43:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}{\fad(0,200)}Shaking!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.74,0:43:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFF8080&}{\fad(0,200)}Dead Scream!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.37,0:43:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是白費力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:58.34,0:44:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪之舞姬啊  慢慢地折磨  別立刻把她們凍死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.64,0:44:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}Burning…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.77,0:44:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}{\fad(0,200)}Mandala!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.23,0:44:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.74,0:44:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來幾個都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:21.57,0:44:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好陪她們玩吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.79,0:44:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}Shine Aqua…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.96,0:44:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&HFDC228&}{\fad(0,300)}Illusion!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.05,0:44:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}Venus…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.26,0:44:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}{\fad(0,200)}Love Me Chain!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:50.85,0:44:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}Sparkling…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.10,0:44:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H37DB00&}{\fad(0,200)}Wide Pressure!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.21,0:45:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病成那樣還跑出去!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.71,0:45:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:21.38,0:45:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子…不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:24.30,0:45:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰雪竹姬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:26.64,0:45:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正準備要…冰凍這個地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.94,0:45:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰來…把冰雪竹姬的事告訴姬子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.32,0:45:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H96BB00&}Deep…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.61,0:45:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H2626FF&}Fire…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.41,0:45:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H1C71FD&}Crescent…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.07,0:45:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H74A5FA&}World…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.22,0:46:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水手戰士們  果然撐不了太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.60,0:46:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就到此為止吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.58,0:46:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我慢著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:15.90,0:46:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來者何人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:19.32,0:46:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:22.82,0:46:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水手戰士們的最後壓軸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:26.99,0:46:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣  是不是很美啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.74,0:46:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球即將變成冰雪的世界  並成為我的收藏品之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.21,0:46:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收藏品?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:36.71,0:46:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可沒興趣變成妳的擺飾  真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.59,0:46:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在永不融化的冰雪中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:49.89,0:46:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠的沈睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:52.27,0:46:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永無紛擾  安穩寂靜的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:57.31,0:46:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太美好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.61,0:47:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒絕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:02.28,0:47:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們…不管是戀愛或是失戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.66,0:47:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.00,0:47:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}翔…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.41,0:47:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為單戀所苦  好幾個晚上睡不著覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.38,0:47:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然充滿著這些痛苦、悲傷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.21,0:47:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也正因為如此我們才有「活著」的感受!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:29.89,0:47:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有所痛苦  但是在熬過去之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:35.73,0:47:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸福的時刻必定會到來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.10,0:47:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凡是忤逆我的傢伙  全都得結成冰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:49.24,0:47:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙是屬於我一個人的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.33,0:47:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像妳這麼自私  愛著一個人有多美好妳是不會懂的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:58.79,0:48:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會怎樣都無所謂  只要可以救翔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.80,0:48:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Crisis～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.80,0:48:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,200)}Make Up!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.19,0:48:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.90,0:48:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}如果我是人類女孩的話  就會為了他變成竹姬…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.06,0:49:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Rainbow…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:03.73,0:49:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}Moon…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.53,0:49:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\c&H00FFFF&}{\fad(0,200)}Heart Ache!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:27.80,0:49:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次我不會再手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.22,0:49:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為很美的那個冰雪世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:35.35,0:49:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是死的世界啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:36.72,0:49:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看起來好像很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:38.43,0:49:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我幫妳解脫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:51.28,0:49:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全死寂的世界  根本沒有美可言!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:59.41,0:50:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Super Sailor Moon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.95,0:50:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用魔幻銀水晶的話  妳會死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.42,0:50:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不能讓她死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.50,0:50:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一起守護她!
