Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:38.91,0:50:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.58,0:50:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位…
