Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:51.50,0:52:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}拜託…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.79,0:52:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}即使只有一晚{\i0}
