Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:58.01,0:52:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}變成竹姬吧!{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.43,0:53:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:52.64,0:53:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是竹姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.02,0:53:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竹姬…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:03.99,0:54:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:05.03,0:54:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在在太空中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.71,0:54:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.88,0:54:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是日出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.50,0:54:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然可以看到這樣的景色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:27.01,0:54:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.90,0:54:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}翔  我終於來到這裡了{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:39.61,0:54:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}在這美麗的太空{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.19,0:54:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}看著地球的日出{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:48.24,0:54:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}女神?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.79,0:54:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}月亮的女神嗎?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.16,0:54:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\i1}翔  果真如你所說…{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.38,0:54:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要活下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.80,0:55:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屬於你的竹姬  在降落地球的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:04.17,0:55:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必須在那裡迎接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:07.26,0:55:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必須為了愛著你的人好好活著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:16.44,0:55:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的夢想實現了  謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:19.23,0:55:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:20.77,0:55:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法永遠待在你的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:26.45,0:55:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛你  我的太空少年…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.59,0:55:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:46.01,0:55:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小兔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.97,0:55:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.15,0:56:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名夜竹小姐  請問您對這次航行的感想是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:05.49,0:56:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.03,0:56:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請告訴我們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:07.03,0:56:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一句話也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:08.74,0:56:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月亮上真的有竹姬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:12.03,0:56:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.12,0:56:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是您想出來的笑話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:16.21,0:56:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次航行的印象…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:26.13,0:56:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.18,0:56:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬子…
